<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink394">
<l>māṇpil koḷkaiyoṭu mayaṅkutuyar ceyta</l>
<l>vaṉpi laṟaṉu maruḷiṟṟu maṉṟa</l>
<l>veñcura miṟanta vañci lōtip</l>
<l>perumaṭa māṉpiṇai yalaitta</l>
<l>ciṟunutaṟ kuṟumakaṭ kāṭṭiya vammē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Even law of virtue which lacks in kindness </l>
<l>and which caused me distressing grief, </l>
<l>along with its inglorious principles,  </l>
<l>has indeed shown favour [to me]!</l>
<l>Come so that I can show you</l> 
<l>[my] little daughter with small forehead </l>
<l>who frolicked like a very naïve doe,</l>
<l>that girl of beautiful, delicate hair</l>
<l>who had traversed the hot desert. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
